#: aiogram.methods.send_message_draft.SendMessageDraft:1 of
msgid ""
"Use this method to stream a partial message to a user while the message "
"is being generated. Note that the streamed draft is ephemeral and acts as"
" a temporary 30-second preview - once the output is finalized, you "
"**must** call :class:`aiogram.methods.send_message.SendMessage` with the "
"complete message to persist it in the user's chat. Returns :code:`True` "
"on success."
msgstr ""

#: aiogram.methods.send_message_draft.SendMessageDraft:3 of
msgid "Source: https://core.telegram.org/bots/api#sendmessagedraft"
msgstr ""

